sources.title: Virus - Fukkatsu No Hi
sources.description: This is Virus (Fukkatsu No Hi) separated into DVD5 files. Download all of the files (not including the cover.jpg) and burn them to a single layer DVD in a folder named VIDEO_TS, also create an empty folder named AUDIO_TS. I created this using DVDShrink and the source files found here: http://www.archive.org/details/Virus_Fukkatsu_no_hi The subtitles have been changed to be yellow instead of green.
